babel compile command:

babel src/app.js --out-file=public/scripts/app.js --presets=env,react

Add watch flag to watch for changes:

babel src/app.js --out-file=public/scripts/app.js --presets=env,react --watch

use a separate tab in command line terminal to run live-server public

React synthetic events docs:  https://reactjs.org/docs/events.html  handle forms, etc.

React component classes have to include a render method.

let list = ['name', 'email', 'password'];

is password in the list?

list.indexOf('password') > -1 ? true : false

